{"tid":1980681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【粉絲心痛】18歲本田仁美地獄式節食 搣甩包包面自信晒馬甲線","createTime":"2020-04-20T08:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:24:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb41c610f9805afeeeef9d075881634a1e63c0f3","tid":1980681,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"日本女子組合AKB48成員本田仁美，前年參加韓國Mnet人氣選秀節目《PRODUCE 101》，最終排名第九位，與同門的宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子組成12人K-pop女團IZ*ONE。<br />\n<br />\n年僅18歲的本田仁美，自從攻韓後便積極減肥，她去年為搣甩baby fat而進行地獄式節食法，一天只吃一包蝦條，另外再配合運動，上月已成功減去近20磅。本田仁美似乎未有鬆懈，本田仁美目前仍努力做運動，見她登上韓國健身中心的IG，露腰大晒馬甲線，還擺出高難度體操動作，從照片所見，本田仁美成功改善包包面，不過一班日本粉絲就表示感到心痛，認為以前肥肥白白的本田仁美較為可愛。事實上，本田仁美近月來被指減肥過度，由於四肢過於纖瘦，望落似足「骷髏骨」，令人擔心其健康，希望她不要再瘦下去。"},{"pid":"59b08f1f52b810c22089bf9b72e6a93876d30f96","tid":1980681,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/124eJV5m1UGitZ787tdKQfv3ePY=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/S4H6JXG5IFS2DDXGCY7VNOMVCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F124eJV5m1UGitZ787tdKQfv3ePY%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FS4H6JXG5IFS2DDXGCY7VNOMVCE.jpg&h=89e6f444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18歲本田仁美赴韓發展後積極減肥。"},{"pid":"b56834e28bf4092095dbb3ade3b61b028d09148a","tid":1980681,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"18歲已經有腹肌, 相反港男......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214ff6b445cc4b018572a4c434057d624d8f8e31","tid":1980681,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"太瘦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec0816b3cab2f5a9549c54a39b2179dc9a7c06","tid":1980681,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike"